nodes.text: Star Wars: The Clone Wars: Darth Maul Returns

Star Wars: The Clone Wars: Darth Maul Returns is a DVD Director's Cut edit of the final four episodes of Season Four of Star Wars: The Clone Wars: "Massacre," "Bounty," "Brothers" and "Revenge." It was released on September 11, 2012 exclusively at Target locations, and on January 8, 2013 at other locations.
